How do you handle dynamically changing dates in Selenium?

Answer:

Use Java LocalDate
Generate dynamic future/past date
Extract:
day
month
year
Navigate calendar dynamically
Select generated date
-----------
LocalDate.now()
plusDays()
minusDays()
getDayOfMonth()
getMonth()
getYear()
----------------
Real-Time Example
Flight Booking
Departure = today + 7
Return = today + 15
Use:
LocalDate.now().plusDays(7);
LocalDate.now().plusDays(15);
